This is how to total_match of lst1 and lst2:
   Remember that total1 is 0
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this lst1's length times:
      Remember that total1 is sum of total1 and (item i in lst1's length)
      Increase i
   End do
   Remember that total2 is 0
   Remember that j is 0
   Do this lst2's length times:
      Remember that total2 is sum of total2 and (item j in lst2's length)
      Increase j
   End do
   When total1 is at most total2, then:
      The answer is lst1
   End when
   The answer is lst2
